###  ╩┘└┘┴  └─┘ ┴

    ## Keyboard
    input type:keyboard {
        xkb_layout br
        xkb_numlock enable
    }

    ## Touchpad
    input type:touchpad {
        tap enable
        dwt disabled
        natural_scroll enable
    }

    ## Change cursor
    seat * xcursor_theme default 28

